#: app/templates/help.html:8
msgid ""
"This page provides an overview of key features and direct links to where "
"they can be managed."
msgstr ""
"Wɔ wɔ mpɔnɔa sɛnea ɛwɔ ne nyansa na wɔdze asɛe yɛn adwumayɛ wɔ sɛ ebiw ho "
"nkwaohyɛnhyɛm."

